        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down</placeName>
                    <date>5 October 1848</date>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
<p>[Thanks his correspondent for informing him of the barnacles and asks that they should be sent directed to him to the Geological Society.]</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        

        

        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">Assistant geologist and artist with the Geological Survey, who had a special interest in palaeontology (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2547.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Flett 1937</ref>). Baily is identified as the recipient in Sotheby’s catalogue.</note>
        </div>        
            
